    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo quinquagesimo quinto, quinto nonus madii,
                        indictione tertia. <persName><name ref="Rodulfus">Rodulfus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Oddo">Oddi</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Inghilenda">Inghilenda</name></persName> iugalis eius et filia
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Nocca">Noche</name></persName> (…)
                            <foreign>offrono</foreign> tibi Deo et <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> et <rs key="#Hospitals">ospitalis</rs>
                            Sancti Iacobi et Sancti Gilii</orgName> de loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/3207" key="#Churches #Hospitals">Altopascio</placeName>
                        idest unam petiam de terra cum <rs key="#Houses">casa solariata</rs> et omni
                        edificio eius, que esse videtur in civitate Luca prope <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3220">ecclesiam Sancti
                            Iuliani</orgName>. Que tenet unum caput in via publica et aliut in terra
                        que fuit quondam <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Wilielmus"
                                >Guilielmi</name></persName> notarii, latus unum tenet in medio muro
                        de casa filiorum quondam <persName><name ref="Gaugus"
                            >Gaughi</name></persName> et aliut latus in medio muro de casa
                                <persName><name ref="Bonaccursus">Bonacorsi</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Peregrinus">Pelegrini</name></persName>. (…)
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in dupplum (…) et insuper penam argenti optimi
                        libras decem. (…) Actum <placeName key="#Houses" ref="#places/4"
                            >Luca</placeName>. (…) (S) Ego <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Heinricus">Henricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> domni imperatoris interfui et subscripsi. Signum
                        manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Cervellatus"
                            >Cervellati</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Hubertus"
                                >Uberti</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Bertolottus">Bertelotti</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Scarota">Scarote</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ribufatus">Ribuffati</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Gotefredus">Gottifredi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bonomus">Bonsomi</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Betto">Betti</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rabaccatus">Rabaccati</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominici</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Montanus">Montani</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberti</name></persName> rogati <rs
                            key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Heinricus">Henricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris post traditam
                        complevi et dedi.</ab> 
                        <ab>Ista vero offersionis cartula tali pacto facta est: si nos qui supra
                        iugales anbo mortui erimus in ac via de Ierusalem quam nos facimus, modo
                        suprascripta cartula statim sit firma et stabilis. Et si aliquo tempore
                        rector suprascripti ospitalis voluerit eam vendere, vendat eam filiis
                        quondam suprascripti Ganghi, si ipsi eam comparare voluerint pro minus sol.
                        decem quam ab alio homine habere potuerit. Et si ipsi infra triginta diebus
                        post inquisitionem sic non comparaverint, exinde vendant cui eis placuerit.
                        Et si quis ex nobis mortuus fuerit, eius portio absolute sit suprascripti
                        ospitalis, et ille qui supervixerit utatur suprascripta portio mortui donec
                        vixerit, et non liceat ei eam vendere vel pignorare aut ullo modo alienare,
                        sed omni tempore sit firma et stabilis ad opus suprascripti ospitalis.
                        (…)</ab>
                </div>
